{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783486602162,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_j0W6TKMK5CVizJSl3K4NKjnb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE|fanout_lineage_artifact_dir|step_resolve_artifact_root|phase_init|execute the research loop","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime","include":"*.cjs"},"output":"Found 9 matches\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/compile-command-contracts.cjs:\n  Line 216:         'config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir',\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs:\n  Line 936:  * with config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir overriding step_resolve_artifact_root.\n\n  Line 967:     `  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: ${lineageDir}`,\n\n  Line 974:     // A research lineage's phase_init binds research_topic from this line. Without it a\n\n  Line 1010:     `The step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to ${lineageDir} via the`,\n\n  Line 1011:     `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node`,\n\n  Line 1014:     `Run phase_init, phase_main_loop (${stopClause}), and phase_synthesis.`,\n\n  Line 1017:     `When complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:${lineage.label}`,\n\n  Line 1055:     `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: ${lineageDir}`,\n","metadata":{"matches":9,"truncated":false},"title":"FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE|fanout_lineage_artifact_dir|step_resolve_artifact_root|phase_init|execute the research loop","time":{"start":1783486602137,"end":1783486602148}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0d9ad6a222379b6a016a4dd88a1cb08191ab1c482acfb23487"}},"id":"prt_f4015db92001v3kFONotdjjgM7","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","messageID":"msg_f4015a2c500108sYLx9h7Nzrjw"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783486602386,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_MdIOvuCnT1k4GCD9i0I5bVAV","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE|fanout_lineage_artifact_dir|Run phase_init","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public","include":"*.{cjs,ts,md,yaml}"},"output":"Found 100 matches (more matches available)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_review.contract.md:\n  Line 223: | `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` | N | internal flag `--fanout-lineage-artifact-dir=PATH` or marker `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` | none | N |\n\n  Line 274:    |-- --fanout-lineage-artifact-dir=PATH -> config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir = PATH (internal single-lineage command invocation only)\n\n  Line 382: - `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` when present\n\n  Line 409:   - \"config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir\"\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/123-agent-loops-improved/review/lineages/glm/.generator/build-iterations.cjs:\n  Line 58:     claim: 'The generated CLI lineage prompt opens with \"You are a ${agentName} agent running a fan-out lineage\" and instructs it to \"Run phase_init, phase_main_loop ... and phase_synthesis\" (fanout-run.cjs:806, 816). For review lineages agentName resolves to \"deep-review\", whose contract (agents/deep-review.md:34, 54-64) states it executes EXACTLY ONE iteration, is LEAF-only, and MUST NOT run the full loop. The prompt therefore contradicts the agent contract it names.',\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_review_confirm.yaml:\n  Line 120:     branch_on: \"config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir\"\n\n  Line 123:         artifact_dir: \"{config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir}\"\n\n  Line 124:   