nly\",\n+    \"iterations/iteration-NNN.md\": \"write-once\",\n+    \"deltas/iter-NNN.jsonl\": \"write-once\"\n+  }\n+}\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+{\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"minIdeaObservations\":2,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T00:00:00Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-6-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-strategy.md\n+# Deep Research Strategy\n+\n+## Research Topic\n+\n+Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\n+\n+## Known Context\n+\n+- Target spec folder: `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research`.\n+- Artifact dir is explicitly bound by `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir`; `resolveArtifactRoot` was not run.\n+- `resource-map.md not present; skipping coverage gate`.\n+- This lineage is read-only with respect to source code and spec docs; writes are restricted to this lineage artifact dir.\n+- Parent phase says the merge should rename `deep-loop-workflows` to `system-deep-loop`, nest `deep-loop-runtime` as `runtime/`, preserve `/deep:*` commands and agent names, repair both relative-path directions, migrate advisor/doctor/agent/docs references, and leave fallback-router wiring optional.\n+\n+## Key Questions\n+\n+- [ ] Is the proposed `system-deep-loop/runtime/` structural layout correct, or does it create mode/skill identity ambiguity?\n+- [ ] Are the Class A and Class B path-repair rules complete and directionally correct for live source files and tests?\n+- [ ] Is the `system-spec-kit` tooling-borrow repair correctly scoped to phase 002, and are there hidden borrow paths beyond the four planned files?\n+- [ ] Is the external reference migration plan complete across commands, agents, READMEs, hooks, advisor corpus, skill graph, generated contracts, and examples?\n+- [ ] Should `fallback-router.ts` be wired now for GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback, or remain optional/deferred?\n+\n+## Answered Questions\n+\n+- None yet.\n+\n+## What Worked\n+\n+- Initial packet read established the scoped design, phase sequence, and no-code-change requirement for this lineage.\n+\n+## What Failed\n+\n+- None yet.\n+\n+## Exhausted Approaches\n+\n+- None yet.\n+\n+## Ruled-Out Directions\n+\n+- Implementing merge/fallback changes during this research lineage is out of scope.\n+\n+## Non-Goals\n+\n+- Do not modify source code, command assets, agents, specs outside this lineage, or routing corpus files.\n+- Do not rename `/deep:*` commands or agent names as part of the recommendation unless evidence shows a blocking contradiction.\n+\n+## Stop Conditions\n+\n+- Stop after legal convergence once all key questions have evidence-backed answers and at least three iterations have run, or at `maxIterations=10`.\n+\n+## Next Focus\n+\n+Structural layout and identity model: validate that nesting runtime under a renamed hub as `system-deep-loop/runtime/` is the least-risk layout and that `runtime/` should not be a mode packet.\n+\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-findings-registry.json\n+{\n+  \"openQuestions\": [\n+    \"Is the proposed system-deep-loop/runtime/ structural layout correct, or does it create mode/skill identity ambiguity?\",\n+    \"Are the Class A and Class B path-repair rules complete and directionally correct for live source files and tests?\",\n+    \"Is the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow repair correctly scoped to phase 002, and are there hidden borrow paths beyond the four planned files?\",\n+    \"Is the external reference migration plan complete across commands, agents, READMEs, hooks, advisor corpus, skill graph, generated contracts, and examples?\",\n+    \"Should fallback-router.ts be wired now for GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback, or remain optional/deferred?\"\n+  ],\n+  \"resolvedQuestions\": [],\n+  \"keyFindings\": [],\n+  \"ruledOutDirections\": [],\n+  \"observedIdeas\": [],\n+  \"promotedIdeas\": [],\n+  \"suppressedIdeas\": [],\n+  \"rejectedPatterns\": [],\n+  \"suppressedCandidates\": [],\n+  \"metrics\": {\n+    \"iterationsCompleted\": 0,\n+    \"openQuestions\": 5,\n+    \"resolvedQuestions\": 0,\n+    \"keyFindings\": 0,\n+    \"convergenceScore\": 0,\n+    \"coverageBySources\": {}\n+  }\n+}\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n+# Deep Research Dashboard\n+\n+## Iteration Table\n+\n+| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n+|---:|---|---:|---:|---|\n+\n+## Q