e research and review carry bounded context snapshots. Per-mode convergence, state, artifacts, and tool-permission contracts are preserved unflattened; the three-tier discriminator (workflowMode / runtimeLoopType / backendKind) keeps graph-backed modes and improvement-host/external-adapter modes distinct.\",\n146:     \"source_docs\": [\n147:       \"SKILL.md\",\n148:       \"README.md\",\n149:       \"mode-registry.json\",\n150:       \"deep-research/SKILL.md\",\n151:       \"deep-review/SKILL.md\",\n152:       \"deep-ai-council/SKILL.md\",\n153:       \"deep-improvement/SKILL.md\"\n154:     ],\n155:     \"created_at\": \"2026-06-15T00:00:00Z\",\n156:     \"last_updated_at\": \"2026-07-08T03:29:41Z\"\n157:   }\n158: }\n\n(End of file - total 158 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"schema_version\": 2,\n  \"skill_id\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n  \"family\": \"deep-loop\",\n  \"category\": \"workflow\",\n  \"importance_tier\": \"important\",\n  \"edges\": {\n    \"depends_on\": [\n      {\n        \"target\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n        \"weight\": 0.8,\n        \"context\": \"consumes the frozen MCP-free backend (executor, coverage-graph, scoring, fan-out, council primitives, promoted plumbing) for every mode\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"target\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n        \"weight\": 0.6,\n        \"context\": \"spec-folder workflow, artifact-root topology, and command YAML consumers\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"enhances\": [","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/graph-metadata.json","text":"{\n  \"schema_version\": 2,\n  \"skill_id\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n  \"family\": \"deep-loop\",\n  \"category\": \"workflow\",\n  \"importance_tier\": \"important\",\n  \"edges\": {\n    \"depends_on\": [\n      {\n        \"target\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n        \"weight\": 0.8,\n        \"context\": \"consumes the froze