air, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"minIdeaObservations\":2,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T00:00:00Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-6-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl","text":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop: structural layout, bidirectional path-coupling repair, the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus, and whether fallback-router.ts should be wired for real GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback.\",\"maxIterations\":10,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"convergence\",\"minIdeaObservations\":2,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T00:00:00Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55-fast-6-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":1,"totalLines":1,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1783486764707,"end":1783486764712}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0bbc1e8a43b977e0016a4dd92c9ea88191996df7b2eb3415a8"}},"id":"prt_f4018569f0015QE930t4NKoJdU","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","messageID":"msg_f401822f5001jZUglwzq5tHo63"}}
