{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487301570,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"id":"prt_f40200eaf001n9zRHIONm2neDs","messageID":"msg_f401f2afa001FKGQ1tEwfEdlJ6","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Run detached deep-research fanout lineage `gpt55-fast-6` for deep-loop unification reference research through convergence/max-10 and synthesis.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Artifact boundary: write only under `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6`.\n- Do not touch paths outside the lineage artifact dir.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to the `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` override.\n- Detached OpenCode lineage, not parent self-invocation.\n- Session id: `fanout-gpt55-fast-6-1783486518892-2qss01`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`.\n- Loop type: `research`; `config.stopPolicy: convergence`; `config.maxIterations: 10`.\n- Must run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop`, then `phase_synthesis`.\n- Final completion output for actual finished run: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-6`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded deep-research workflow contract and supporting refs.\n- Confirmed lineage dir existed and was empty.\n- Created lineage subdirs: `iterations/`, `deltas/`, `prompts/`.\n- Created init artifacts:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deep-research-strategy.md`\n  - `deep-research-findings-registry.json`\n  - `deep-research-dashboard.md`\n- Completed and recorded Iteration 1:\n  - `iterations/iteration-001.md`\n  - `deltas/iter-001.jsonl`\n  - Focus: structural layout and identity model.\n  - Finding: `system-deep-loop/runtime/` is coherent if `runtime/` remains infrastructure, not a workflow mode.\n- Completed and recorded Iteration 2:\n  - `iterations/iteration-002.md`\n  - `deltas/iter-002.jsonl`\n  - Focus: bidirectional path-coupling repair.\n  - Finding: Class A/Class B path-direction rules are correct, but inventory needs additions.\n- Completed and recorded Iteration 3:\n  - `iterations/iteration-003.md`\n  - `deltas/iter-003.jsonl`\n  - Focus: `system-spec-kit` tooling borrow.\n  - Finding: four planned edits are necessary but incomplete for phase-002 gates.\n\n### In Progress\n- Iteration 4 research on external reference migration completeness.\n- Evidence gathered but `iteration-004.md` / `iter-004.jsonl` not yet written.\n- `deep-research-dashboard.md` still needs iteration updates.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Treat `runtime/` as nested infrastructure, not a mode packet.\n- Fresh-author unified `system-deep-loop/graph-metadata.json`; do not merge old hub/runtime graph files.\n- Do not use blind find/replace; classify executable imports, fixtures, generated contracts, advisor labels, and historical prose separately.\n- Phase 002 should also cover:\n  - `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/scripts/replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs`\n  - explicit deep-review shims\n  - classified runtime unit-test inventory\n  - `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs`\n  - `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/artifact-root.vitest.ts`\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/council-playbook-anchor-integrity.vitest.ts`\n- Do not decouple runtime from `system-spec-kit` TypeScript tooling during this merge; repair path depth only.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Write Iteration 4 artifacts for external migration findings.\n- Update JSONL state, strategy, registry, and dashboard after Iteration 4.\n- Run Iteration 5 on fallback-router wiring:\n  - inspect `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts`\n  - inspect `fallback-router` tests\n  - inspect `fanout-pool.cjs` retry/failure path\n  - decide whether GLM-5.2 → MiMo-v2.5-Pro wiring should land now or remain optional.\n- Continue iterations until legal convergence or max 10.\n- Run phase synthesis and write final `research.md`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- After Iteration 3 registry metrics: `iterationsCompleted=3`, `openQuestions=2`, `resolvedQuestions=3`, `keyFindings=7`.\n- Remaining open questions:\n  - external reference migration completeness\n  - fallback-router real wiring decision\n- `resource-map.md` is absent; coverage gate was skipped.\n- External migration evidence gathered:\n  - `rg -l \"deep-loop-workflows|deep-loop-runtime\" \".opencode\" \".claude\" \".github\" ...` returned `781` live hits excluding specs/node_modules/dist/artifact.\n  - Advisor plan paths are partly stale:\n    - missing: `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/skill_advisor/generated/aliases.ts`\n    - actual: `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts`\n    - missing: `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/skill_advisor/scorer/explicit.ts`\n    - actual: `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/lanes/explicit.ts`\n  - `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py` still has `MODE_REGISTRY_PATH` and `MERGED_DEEP_SKILL_ID = \"deep-loop-workflows\"`.\n  - `.opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js:35` hardcodes `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json`.\n  - `.github/workflows/agent-mirror-sync.yml:17` hardcodes old checker path.\n  - Graph metadata migration list should include `sk-prompt`; it also points at `deep-loop-workflows`.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6`: lineage artifact boundary.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl`: append-only state log with config + 3 iterations.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-strategy.md`: current plan/open questions.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-findings-registry.json`: resolved/open question registry.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/plan.md`: structural merge plan under review.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md`: reference migration plan under review.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/004-fallback-router-wiring/plan.md`: optional fallback-router plan.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md`: hub identity/invariants evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json`: mode registry and advisor projection source.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs`: hidden `system-spec-kit` seam.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/scripts/replay-graph-from-artifacts.cjs`: unlisted internal path-coupling site.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py`: advisor routing constants.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts`: actual alias projection file.\n- `.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/lanes/explicit.ts`: actual explicit scoring lane.\n- `.opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js`: plugin registry path.\n- `.github/workflows/agent-mirror-sync.yml`: CI checker path.","time":{"start":1783487270575,"end":1783487301565},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ca41f19899dbc7b016a4ddb2692fc8191bf8dc31150f6910e","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
