{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487333807,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_z162ocOcdpVxPILEGEohiJ7H","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md","offset":1,"limit":240},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Deep Research Dashboard\n2: \n3: ## Iteration Table\n4: \n5: | run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n6: |---:|---|---:|---:|---|\n7: \n8: ## Question Status\n9: \n10: 0 / 5 answered.\n11: \n12: ## Convergence Trend\n13: \n14: No iterations yet.\n15: \n16: ## Dead Ends\n17: \n18: - None yet.\n19: \n20: ## Blocked Stops\n21: \n22: - None.\n23: \n24: ## Graph Convergence\n25: \n26: - Not evaluated for this detached lineage.\n27: \n28: ## Next Focus\n29: \n30: Structural layout and identity model.\n\n(End of file - total 30 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Deep Research Dashboard\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n|---:|---|---:|---:|---|\n\n## Question Status\n\n0 / 5 answered.\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\nNo iterations yet.\n\n## Dead Ends\n\n- None yet.\n\n## Blocked Stops","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md","text":"# Deep Research Dashboard\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings count | status |\n|---:|---|---:|---:|---|\n\n## Question