{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487386347,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"id":"prt_f4021bdd6001D1cWVVBhuQNU2H","messageID":"msg_f4021a1e8001pdxSJsjWb4rNMu","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","type":"text","text":"Current evidence shows the 003 plan already includes several items the prior summary treated as gaps, including `sk-prompt` graph metadata and the pre-commit/GitHub Actions mirror checker pair. I’m adjusting Iteration 4 to reflect the current plan, not stale assumptions.","time":{"start":1783487380950,"end":1783487386343},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02d18bd393e4833f016a4ddb94f3c88191b43b37a5f127d40e","phase":"commentary"}}}}
