rn/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 199:     \"causal_summary\": \"`deep-loop-workflows` is the framework's first parent-skill-with-nested-mode-packets, and Phases 1–2 proved the pattern and Phase 3 implemented its routing optimization\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 35:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 40:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 55:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 75:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/120-glm-5-2-support/002-framework-bakeoff/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 42:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/model_benchmark/benchmark-profiles/glm-5.2-frameworks.json\",\n\n  Line 52:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/assets/model_benchmark/benchmark-profiles/glm-5.2-frameworks.json\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/117-parent-nested-skill-pattern/002-advisor-routing-drift-guard/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 16:       \"deep-loop-workflows routing parity test\",\n\n  Line 35:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 44:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 58:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 200:     \"causal_summary\": \"`mode-registry.json` claimed to be the single source of truth for how each deep-loop-workflows mode routes, but the advisor never read it — the mode projection was hardcoded in two places with three different cardinalities (Python `DEEPROUTINGMODEBYKEY` = 3, TS `DEEPMODEBYCANONICAL` = 4, registry = 8 modes)\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/117-parent-nested-skill-pattern/001-rename-fix-and-shared-decision/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 14:       \"deep-loop-workflows folder rename fix\",\n\n  Line 16:       \"shared stays in deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 17:       \"deep-loop-workflows rename fix plan\",\n\n  Line 20:       \"deep-loop-workflows rename fix tasks\",\n\n  Line 23:       \"deep-loop-workflows rename fix checklist\",\n\n  Line 28:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 44:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 45:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs\",\n\n  Line 58:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 64:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs\",\n\n  Line 200:     \"causal_summary\": \"The 152 merge wired `deep-loop-workflows`'s internal references to bare packet names (`context/`, `research/`, `review/`, `improvement/`, `ai-council/`)\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/117-parent-nested-skill-pattern/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 20:       \"deep-loop-workflows nested skill pattern\",\n\n  Line 28:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 129:     \"causal_summary\": \"The 152 epic merged five deep-loop skills into one `deep-loop-workflows` skill structured as a thin hub `SKILL.md` + `mode-registry.json` + five internal mode packets, with the packets deliberately non-discoverable (one advisor identity)\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 31:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 3:   \"skill_id\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 10:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 29:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 43:     \"depends_on\": [\"deep-loop-runtime\"],\n\n  Line 72:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 102:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 117:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 118:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 119:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 120:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 121:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 122:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 123:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/shared/synthesis/resource-map.cjs\"\n\n  Line 127:         \"name\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 129:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 135:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\",\n\n  Line 139:         \"name\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 141:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 145:     \"causal_summary\": \"deep-loop-workflows is the single public skill that merges active deep-loop persona modes (deep-research, deep-review, deep-ai-council, deep-improvement) into one advisor identity with active mode packets, routed by workflowMode through mode-registry.json over the frozen MCP-free deep-loop-runtime backend. @context owns one-shot retrieval while research and review carry bounded context snapshots. Per-mode convergence, state, artifacts, and tool-permission contracts are preserved unflattened; the three-tier discriminator (workflowMode / runtimeLoopType / backendKind) keeps graph-backed modes and improvement-host/external-adapter modes distinct.\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/999-sk-doc-parent/022-parent-skill-logic-review/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 192:     \"causal_summary\": \"The parent-hub (parent-skill) pattern — one advisor identity, a `mode-registry.json`, a `hub-router.json`, one `graph-metadata.json`, and nested mode/surface packets — is scaffolded by `create-skill` and implemented independently by four hubs (sk-doc, sk-code, sk-design, deep-loop-workflows) and consumed by the skill advisor\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/999-sk-doc-parent/011-smart-router-alignment/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 194:     \"causal_summary\": \"Roughly 24 skills across the repo carry router pseudocode or keyed routing logic inside their `SKILL.md`, but only the handful of full parent hubs (`sk-code`, `sk-design`, `deep-loop-workflows`, `sk-doc`) follow the canonical 4-pattern smart-router contract documented at `.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-skill/assets/skill/skillsmartrouter.md`\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-speckit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/003-memory-and-causal-runtime/003-embedder-testing-and-architecture/009-memory-leak-remediation/014-fix-deep-review-p1-findings-for-lifecycle-and-sidecar-hardening/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 53:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/loop-lock.vitest.ts\",\n\n  Line 113:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/loop-lock.vitest.ts\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/114-operate-like-fable-5/003-measurement-baseline/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 46:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/post-dispatch-validate.ts\",\n\n  Line 75:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/post-dispatch-validate.ts\",\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/graph-metadata.json:\n  Line 4:   \"skill_id\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 18:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 23:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 28:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 35:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 40:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 45:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 53:         \"target\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 55:         \"context\": \"frozen MCP-free backend that deep-loop-workflows consumes for every mode\"\n\n  Line 64:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 65:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 66:       \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 82:     \"deep-loop-runtime skill\",\n\n  Line 91:       \"deep-loop-runtime skill\",\n\n  Line 98:       \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 120:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 121:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/README.md\",\n\n  Line 122:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/executor-config.ts\",\n\n  Line 123:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-db.ts\",\n\n  Line 124:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/council/multi-seat-dispatch.cjs\",\n\n  Line 125:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/council/round-state-jsonl.cjs\",\n\n  Line 126:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/council/adjudicator-verdict-scoring.cjs\",\n\n  Line 127:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/council/cost-guards.cjs\",\n\n  Line 128:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/council/session-state-hierarchy.cjs\",\n\n  Line 129:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/convergence.cjs\",\n\n  Line 130:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/lib/cli-guards.cjs\",\n\n  Line 131:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/database/deep-loop-graph.sqlite\",\n\n  Line 132:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/executor-config.vitest.ts\",\n\n  Line 133:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/council/multi-seat-dispatch.vitest.ts\",\n\n  Line 134:       \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/council/round-state-jsonl.vitest.ts\"\n\n  Line 138:         \"name\": \"deep-loop-runtime\",\n\n  Line 140:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 146:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-db.ts\",\n\n  Line 150:         \"name\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 152:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 156:         \"name\": \"deep-loop-workflows\",\n\n  Line 158:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md\",\n\n  Line 164:         \"path\": \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/convergence.cjs\",\n\n\n(Results truncated. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":100,"truncated":true},"title":"deep-loop-workflows|deep-loop-runtime","time":{"start":1783487394579,"end":1783487394640}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_072932b5fb4cc726016a4ddba28a608191a76ccf15e6ca9e95"}},"id":"prt_f4021f311001k5UOToRRNIaO0J","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","messageID":"msg_f4021d5ca001mC7g1OtOzhQTVl"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783487394713,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"glob","callID":"call_nndSqvBhwXpdS61gdLhcGM7z","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"**/parent-skill-check.cjs","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode"},"output":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/doctor/scripts/parent-skill-check.cjs","metadata":{"count":1,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode","time":{"start":1783487394570,"end":1783487394712}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_072932b5fb4cc726016a4ddba28a3881919361688be8d467e1"}},"id":"prt_f4021f2f5001sjIT8DUuyWmGDn","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","messageID":"msg_f4021d5ca001mC7g1OtOzhQTVl"}}
