us, skill graph, generated contracts, and examples?\",\n+      \"answer\": \"The child 003 plan is directionally complete across the major live surfaces; it should preserve category staging, synchronize advisor codegen/drift guards, regenerate compiled command contracts, and dedupe literal graph-edge duplicates such as cli-opencode.\"\n     }\n   ],\n   \"keyFindings\": [\n     {\n@@ -58,8 +61,32 @@\n       \"id\": \"gpt55-fast-6-f007\",\n       \"title\": \"test:council needs council-playbook-anchor-integrity path updates\",\n       \"summary\": \"The test:council script includes council-playbook-anchor-integrity, which hardcodes deep-loop-runtime test paths and regexes.\",\n       \"sources\": [\"file:.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/package.json:31\", \"file:.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/council-playbook-anchor-integrity.vitest.ts:27\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"gpt55-fast-6-f008\",\n+      \"title\": \"External migration plan is directionally complete and category-driven\",\n+      \"summary\": \"The 003 plan covers hardcoded constants, structured identity fields, codegen, command assets, docs, graph metadata, examples, advisor corpus, and final verification as separate categories.\",\n+      \"sources\": [\"file:.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:75\", \"file:.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/plan.md:106\"]\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"id\": \"gpt55-fast-6-f009\",\n+      \"title\": \"Advisor projection migration must be synchronized\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Python, TypeScript scorer files, and the drift guard all hardcode the merged deep skill identity and registry/projection contract.\",\n+      \"sources\": [\"file:.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/scripts/skill_advisor.py:83\", \"file:.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/lib/scorer/aliases.ts:109\", \"file:.opencode/skill