{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487660773,"sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","part":{"id":"prt_f4026021f0015CtTtCYTdXXyFz","messageID":"msg_f4025b52c001JXwY0p35zE5szQ","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","type":"text","text":"Iteration 5 decision is evidence-backed: fallback routing is real and tested, but wiring it is a separate feature and the current optional plan points too low in the stack. I’m recording that as the last key-question answer.","time":{"start":1783487660575,"end":1783487660771},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0bd7fbb6e2fc2c86016a4ddcac8b188191951f83b6afc75478","phase":"commentary"}}}}
