===================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n@@ -7,21 +7,24 @@\n | 1 | Structural layout and identity model | 0.90 | 5 | complete |\n | 2 | Bidirectional path-coupling repair | 0.85 | 6 | complete |\n | 3 | System-spec-kit tooling borrow and hidden seams | 0.80 | 6 | complete |\n | 4 | External reference migration completeness | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n+| 5 | Fallback-router real wiring decision | 0.75 | 5 | complete |\n \n ## Question Status\n \n-4 / 5 answered.\n+5 / 5 answered.\n \n ## Convergence Trend\n \n-0.90 -> 0.85 -> 0.80 -> 0.70. Latest iteration still above the 0.05 convergence threshold because one key question remains open.\n+0.90 -> 0.85 -> 0.80 -> 0.70 -> 0.75. All key questions are answered; one low-novelty convergence validation pass remains before synthesis.\n \n ## Dead Ends\n \n - Treating raw old-name grep results as directly actionable is a dead end; categories need separate handling.\n - Hand-editing compiled command contracts is ruled out; regenerate them from source command assets.\n+- Treating fallback-router wiring as a mandatory merge dependency is ruled out.\n+- Wiring model-aware fallback directly into the generic pool without an explicit hook is ruled out.\n \n ## Blocked Stops\n \n - None.\n@@ -31,5 +34,5 @@\n - Not evaluated for this detached lineage.\n \n ## Next Focus\n \n-Fallback-router real wiring decision.\n+Convergence validation and synthesis readiness.\n","additions":6,"deletions":3}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/iterations/iteration-005.md\nA .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deltas/iter-005.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-strategy.md\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-findings-registry.json\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1783487790109,"end":1783487790118}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c857970b112675a016a4ddcb2d8f88191a19c38797f4e456b"}},"id":"prt_f40261aa9001rMUZBaT4ngMBJF","sessionID":"ses_0bfeb66cbffe4XyuwEMaxiBvG7","messageID":"msg_f40260b97001QA33kgUueQrPTk"}}
