/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md:13\"]\n   }\n ],\n \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n   {\n@@ -143,21 +149,25 @@\n   },\n   {\n     \"approach\": \"Wire model substitution directly into the generic pool without a hook\",\n     \"reason\": \"fanout-pool.cjs only owns generic items/retries; model-aware command construction and lineage context live in fanout-run.cjs.\"\n+  },\n+  {\n+    \"approach\": \"Continue to max-10 after all questions are answered\",\n+    \"reason\": \"The configured stop policy is convergence, the minimum iteration count is satisfied, and no blocked stop remains.\"\n   }\n ],\n \"observedIdeas\": [],\n \"promotedIdeas\": [],\n \"suppressedIdeas\": [],\n \"rejectedPatterns\": [],\n \"suppressedCandidates\": [],\n \"metrics\": {\n-  \"iterationsCompleted\": 5,\n+  \"iterationsCompleted\": 6,\n   \"openQuestions\": 0,\n   \"resolvedQuestions\": 5,\n-  \"keyFindings\": 16,\n-  \"convergenceScore\": 0.95,\n+  \"keyFindings\": 17,\n+  \"convergenceScore\": 1,\n   \"coverageBySources\": {\n     \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md\": 4,\n     \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json\": 3,\n     \".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/graph-metadata.json\": 2,\n","additions":13,"deletions":3},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md","type":"update","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-dashboard.md\n@@ -8,16 +8,17 @@\n | 2 | Bidirectional path-coupling repair | 0.85 | 6 | complete |\n | 3 | System-spec-kit tooling borrow and hidden seams | 0.80 | 6 | complete |\n | 4 | External reference migration completeness | 0.70 | 5 | complete |\n | 5 | Fallback-router real wiring decision | 0.75 | 5 | complete |\n+| 6 | Convergence validation and synthesis readiness | 0.02 | 3 | thought |\n \n ## Question Status\n \n 5 / 5 answered.\n \n ## Convergence Trend\n \n-0.90 -> 0.85 -> 0.80 -> 0.70 -> 0.75. All key questions are answered; one low-novelty convergence validation pass remains before synthesis.\n+0.90 -> 0.85 -> 0.80 -> 0.70 -> 0.75 -> 0.02. Legal convergence reached: all key questions answered, min-iteration count satisfied, and no blocked stop remains.\n \n ## Dead Ends\n \n - Treating raw old-name grep results as directly actionable is a dead end; categories need separate handling.\n@@ -34,5 +35,5 @@\n - Not evaluated for this detached lineage.\n \n ## Next Focus\n \n-Convergence validation and synthesis readiness.\n+Phase synthesis.\n","additions":3,"deletions":2}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/iterations/iteration-006.md\nA .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deltas/iter-006.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-6/deep-research-state.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/0